* GameServer
- The HelpViewer is called twice 
   when we click the OK button it appears again
- Running 2 servers in the same PC is forbiden
   A file running-server is created in the $HOME directory when the
   server is running. When we exit the server application, we delete
   this file. 
   ServerLock::lock()
   ServerLock::unlock()
   ServerLock::isLock()

