* v 0.0.5-177
- (16) MCL Items scissor limited to Window right and bottom
- Fix a bug in the item selection rectangle scissor rectangle
- Avoid an arithmetic exception in ScrollBars's moveCursorToValue()
- When hidding a ScrollBar in MML or Window, setting its value to 0
- MCL item scissor rectangle now take care of QuadRenderer's drawing dev
- MCL item have their own scissor rectangle (cut to the left line)
- MCL items left line wasn't cut by scissor rectangle : fixed
- MCL headers wasn't cut by scissor rectangle : fixed
- MCL Headers event handling with scrollbar value added
- MCL Items event handling with scrollbar value added
- MCL scrollbars value computed
- bugfix in the MCL item drawing due to an error in the ItemScissorRectangle 
  computation
- MultiColumnList's left lines correctly drawn
- MultiColumnList column header and items scissor rectangle bug fix
- MultiColumnList now need mParentWindow member
- Resizing window now set the ScrollPane geometry dirty flag to true

* v 0.0.5-176
- PopupMenu drop down effect implemented
- PopupMenuItem mouse over effect implemented
- Hidden column handled when resizing and reordering columns
- MultiColumnList::mLastColumnRight handles hidden columns
- Columns can be shown/hidden
- pmiCheckBox's signal and Column's slot connected
- pmiCheckBox sigValuerChange signal  implementation
- pmiCheckBox toggleCheck works
- PopupMenu::injectMouse() implementation
- PopupMenu can be hidden
- PopupMenu injectMouse implementation
- pmiSeparator is drawn and add to PopupMenu under pmiTitle
- pmiSeparator class implementation
- pmiCheckBox::draw() implementation
- pmiCheckBox implementation
- Fixed the multicolumnlist column left line bug
- pmiTitle drawn
- PopupMenu::makeCorners also compute items absolute corners
- PopupMenu background drawn

